{"tid":1648443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"18區唔係問題，「開花」只係一個代名詞，先係問題。","createTime":"2019-10-12T08:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T09:25:14.000Z","uid":170812,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bf18a875ee28ddf03608fea1bc1692719616d7","tid":1648443,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"根本「開花」係一個代詞，甚至只係一個形容詞，根本<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係一個行動</span></span>。唔應該擺上枱面用黎區吹雞。<br />\n<br />\n你想啲街坊出黎，係要知道出黎做乜！<br />\n「集會、遊行、流水集會、行街、靜坐......」，仲有好多其他字可以用，起碼啲人知出到黎，係有個初步行動目標。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好再用 「開花」 黎代表行動出文宣、出行動post。"},{"pid":"666888bcc53f2a919ddf97251ca03018f5d567cd","tid":1648443,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"efe512a4098414523d7ce129a156dccef5e4a342","tid":1648443,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"8efd65d3fe5a0d02eb3f17a9581651d24ed3c3fb","tid":1648443,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"7329316d49c5524b0762f2ef8bde80dbc503b55e","tid":1648443,"uid":25408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"口講開花，出到黎一班人鳩流流"},{"pid":"258606ba42a2bf60bb3eb473e2cede29306ff9fb","tid":1648443,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"7064f8c3fd104c490f3f91d799283d5c30f5353c","tid":1648443,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01c99bf6ce1dbea52c8c2d9fea1c7bb9cce2cc2","tid":1648443,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa8c5a37719f05b96